title: Chunkzz
subTitle: The lives of four friends Romario, Riyas, Yoodas and Athmaram, take a dramatic turn when a girl joins their mechanical engineering class.

title: Colours
subTitle: Dr. Rajalakshmi enjoys life with her two daughters, Pinki and Pooja. However, when she uncovers a major pharmaceutical fraud, she becomes the target of dangerous enemies determined to silence her.

title: Parava
subTitle: Irshad and Haseeb, two teenage boys from Mattanchery, share a passion for pigeon flying, a local game. Later, Irshad opens up about a tragic incident that ruined many friendships in the neighbourhood.

title: Greetings
subTitle: Gopan falls in love with his neighbour, Sheethal. After learning that Sheetal has a plan to reunite a separated couple, he also pools in ideas, which leads to many unexpected events.

title: Chandrolsavam
subTitle: Sreehari has returned home from Paris after six years. He tries to settle some scores and clear misunderstandings with his old friends before leaving his village.

title: Puthan Panam
subTitle: Nityananda Shenoy, a gangster from Kasaragod, decides to exact revenge on an ex-minister who swindled him right before demonetisation. Meanwhile, Muthuvel and his mother struggle to survive in Kochi.

title: Keshu Ee Veedinte Nadhan
subTitle: The life of an ordinary driver Keshu turns upside down when he wins a lottery worth 12 crores but his morality gets tested.

title: Naran
subTitle: Velayudhan, an orphan, is loved by the villagers as he keeps the village free from unsavoury people and practices. However, an evil moneylender and politician get jealous and try to get rid of him.

title: Thuruppugulan
subTitle: Menon buys land for his five-star hotel and asks his trusted employee, Sreedharan Unnithan, to take its charge. Years later, Unnithan gets Menon imprisoned in a fake case and Kunjumon helps him.

title: Janatha Garage
subTitle: When Anand visits Hyderabad, he encounters Sathyam, who operates an organisation aiding the underprivileged. Sathyam, swayed by Anand's vision, hands over the organisation's management to him.

title: Janatha Garage

title: BOYFRIEND
subTitle: A girl from a wealthy family falls in love with a poor boy from her college. However, things take a turn when her disapproving mother sends thugs to kill her lover.

title: Mizhi Thurakku
subTitle: Savithri's family is attacked, after which she seeks refuge in a man's house. However, she soon experiences the evils of casteism.

title: Theerppu
subTitle: Four friends with a traumatic history reunite at a resort. All hell breaks loose when the group encounters unanticipated repercussions from their past.

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Philips and the Monkey Pen
subTitle: Ryan Philip is a mischieveous 8-year-old, struggles with math- and his strict teacher Pappan. However, everything changes when he discovers a magical pen that helps him solve all his problems.

title: Aravindante Athidhikal
subTitle: After being forsaken by his mother in a temple, Aravindan, a five-year-old boy, is taken in by a hotelier. Against all odds, Aravindan clings to the hope of reuniting with his mother.

title: Christian Brothers
subTitle: When the daughter of a minister gets kidnapped, Christy is called upon to rescue her. Although he manages to save her, he himself gets embroiled in the kidnapper's murder.

title: Varikkuzhiyile Kolapathakam
subTitle: Vincent Kombana, a Parish priest, is highly respected by the people of his village. However, things take an unusual turn after he witnesses a murder.

title: Bahubali-2
subTitle: After learning that his father was brutally killed by Bhallaladeva, Mahendra Baahubali raises an army to defeat him and release his mother from the former's captivity.

title: ABCD
subTitle: Avi and Bhasha are two brothers who enjoy a lavish lifestyle and are later tricked by the former's father into living a life in poverty.

title: ABCD

title: Iruvattom Manavatty
subTitle: During his stint on election duty, a veterinarian, Gautham, meets Bhumika and falls deeply in love. However, Bhumika fears her disapproving father, a staunch communist, finding out.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: Goal
subTitle: Sam, a football player, gets admission in a prestigious international school under sports quota. His life changes for the better when he falls in love with a girl from the same school.

title: Pachakuthira
subTitle: Anandakkuttan's life as a young artist takes a dramatic turn when he takes his autistic brother under his wing, leading to an unexpected yet heartwarming bond between them.

title: Jaya Jaya Jaya Jaya Hey
subTitle: Jayabharathi, an ambitious girl, strives to complete her education. However, when her parents marry her off, she attempts to carve an identity for herself.

title: Vettam
subTitle: Gopalakrishnan meets Veena while trying to smuggle a stolen necklace. Later, he accompanies Veena on her mission to unite with her lover.

title: Mumbai Police
subTitle: ACP Antony Moses has managed to track down his friend's killer when he meets with an accident resulting in partial memory loss. Soon, he is reassigned to investigate the murder and find the culprit.

title: Crazy Gopalan
subTitle: Gopalan, a notorious thief, teams up with Lakshmanan and continues to rob people. Their lives change when they kidnap a rich girl and find themselves trapped.

title: Ring Master
subTitle: Prince, a dog trainer, faces an awkward situation when his pet dog Diana acts in a film alongside his former lover, an actress who shares the same name as the dog.
